<! [CDATA[
 Banano (BAN) Logo
Banano describes itself as a feeless, instant, rich in potassium cryptocurrency powered by directed acyclic graph (DAG) technology that aims to disrupt the meme economy. Banano was a hard fork of Nano coin in 2018. The current team features members that had previously worked at Nano, and are represented by dancing banana avatars on the coin’s website. Banano’s key features include: the block-lettuce, a play on Block lattice, DAG architecture; instant and feeless transactions; fungible tokens; daily airdrops and more.
You can download theBananologo on full-version of the page.
